headline: KEYCORP TO PRESENT AT THE GOLDMAN SACHS FINANCIAL SERVICES CONFERENCE
summary: KeyCorp (NYSE: KEY) announced today that Chris Gorman, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer, will speak at the Goldman Sachs Financial Services Conference on Tuesday, December 9, 2025, at 8:40 a.m. ET in New York City.
